    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "Note that you can workaround this with `cast interface <(cat ./out/Contract.sol/Contract.json | jq .abi)`. A more generalized version is `cast interface <(forge inspect Contract abi)` which will generate the artifacts if not present. But I agree not having to use a workaround like this would be preferable.\r\n\r\n(@gakonst using this as the issue you [requested](https://twitter.com/gakonst/status/1519610516813066241), thanks @SusheendharVijay for beating me too it ðŸ™‚)",
